{"tid":2040194,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雙11西灣河警員開槍案 被槍傷21歲青年被控3罪包括企圖搶劫！","createTime":"2020-05-28T12:00:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T15:38:01.000Z","uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"730220b682a779879ab41e1036b37eca86392ba6","tid":2040194,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T12:00:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa6c56472aeda69a47f0b1c8bceab5ac9fa35e5","tid":2040194,"uid":63113,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T12:01:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TpM6eJs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTpM6eJs.png&h=9cce635b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87b6636886e0f19615b4c14cb09ee9fbaa2c2811","tid":2040194,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T12:02:34.000Z","msg":"去年西灣河中槍青年 下周二提堂<br />\n28.05.2020 19:26<br />\n<br />\n去年11月在西灣河中槍的21歲青年周柏均，及一同被捕20歲男子，被警方落案起訴，下周提堂。警方指，經調查後控以兩人阻差辦公及企圖搶劫，周柏均另外被控一項企圖從合法羈押逃脫罪，下月2日在西九龍裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n事發在去年11月11日早上，有示威者在西灣河堵路，一名警員在清理路障時，向走近的人開三槍，周柏均腹部中槍，經手術後切除右腎和部份肝臟。警方當時指有人企圖搶槍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1292631&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1292631%26csid%3D261_341&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu84e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=a7b78ff8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1292631&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"e7536307d3e1f466e481a31d15ac7258f93f0515","tid":2040194,"uid":198035,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T12:04:17.000Z","msg":"哩d 又唔告暴動？"},{"pid":"e827f4f78bcf7c00be9b7b1c0074e58016fe140a","tid":2040194,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87b6636886e0f19615b4c14cb09ee9fbaa2c2811","tid":2040194,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T12:02:34.000Z","msg":"去年西灣河中槍青年 下周二提堂<br />\n28.05.2020 19:26<br />\n<br />\n去年11月在西灣河中槍的21歲青年周柏均，及一同被捕20歲男子，被警方落案起訴，下周提堂。警方指，經調查後控以兩人阻差辦公及企圖搶劫，周柏均另外被控一項企圖從合法羈押逃脫罪，下月2日在西九龍裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n事發在去年11月11日早上，有示威者在西灣河堵路，一名警員在清理路障時，向走近的人開三槍，周柏均腹部中槍，經手術後切除右腎和部份肝臟。警方當時指有人企圖搶槍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1292631&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1292631%26csid%3D261_341&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLu84e4tfxBia5339duguOAPM%3D&h=a7b78ff8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1292631&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T12:06:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd8524d129dbb4da3e8ca2826ca496cc19ac05b","tid":2040194,"uid":65888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T12:06:27.000Z","msg":"訓左無睇，關家榮一家最近過得好嗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"947f20e668ce0e28348b745bdabe97570594557e","tid":2040194,"uid":75655,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T12:07:01.000Z","msg":"氣軍師免責聲明<br />\n手足風險自行評估<br />\n前線撤退由前線自行決定<br />\n手足被捕或失蹤等與冷氣軍師無關<br />\n軍師無需付上任何責任<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212fa1748d5f666ce5bbc70c8c60eac45297a3fe","tid":2040194,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-28T12:08:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />DLLM <